erturbative phenomena is possible within the\nframework of time-dependent perturbation method, by virtue of the\nnonperturbative inclusion of the laser-electron interaction and time-dependent\noptimization of orbitals.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Aug 2020 05:18:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-18"}
